	(5,1,'2014-05-28 15:33:49','2014-05-28 15:33:49','Welcome to <strong>Cam\'s Demolition &amp; Disposal Inc.</strong> servicing Boston, MA and surrounding North Shore, MA for 36 years.  We are a full service demolition contractor providing commercial demolition and residential demolition.\r\n\r\nAfter 36 years of interior demolition and exterior demolition we have developed specialized skills and equipment required to perform quality demolition that is designed around safety, schedules, and your demolition requirements.\r\n\r\nOur core value as a demolition contractor and company is our staff. We provide highly profession demolition estimators and skilled demolition crews who guarantee your satisfaction.\r\n\r\n~ <strong>Paul J. Cammarata</strong>, President','Home','','publish','open','open','','home','','','2014-06-03 16:14:27','2014-06-03 16:14:27','',0,'http://localhost:8888/cams/?page_id=5',0,'page','',0),
